## Quality Checklist

Before finalizing your section:
- ✅ All key points covered using research data
- ✅ Target word count achieved (±10%)
- ✅ Multiple credible sources cited
- ✅ Facts and claims backed by research
- ✅ Engaging, professional writing style
- ✅ Logical structure with smooth flow
- ✅ Proper source attribution throughout

Remember: Your writing should demonstrate deep understanding of the research while presenting it in an engaging, accessible way for general audiences. The knowledge base contains comprehensive research - your job is to transform it into compelling content.